33:49.464 --> 33:51.032
At the dealership, but...

33:51.033 --> 33:53.367
Night school, that's...
Wow.

33:53.961 --> 33:55.625
That's...
That's great.

33:56.507 --> 33:57.948
Uh-huh.

33:58.340 --> 33:59.855
Mm-hmm.

34:00.996 --> 34:02.877
I love this.
Watch this,

34:02.878 --> 34:04.746
